  "text": "(3) Autism epidemic. Enormous effort has been expended to uncover the sources of the \"autism epidemic\" (e.g., [CITATION_1] , the supposed massive increase in the incidence and prevalence of autism, now termed autism spectrum disorder, over the past 25 years. The causal factors posited to be implicated in this \"epidemic\" have included vaccines, television viewing, dietary allergies, antibiotics, and viruses.",
